LayeredDiGraph Library

This JavaScript library implements various algorithms in order to provide client with layered directed graph visualization(for more information see Implementation Details section).

Table of Contents

    Installation
    Usage
    Implementation Details
    API
    Example
    Testing
    Contributing
    License

Installation

To use this library in your project, you can install it via npm:

bash

npm install Layered-DiGraph

Usage

First, import the library into your project:

javascript



