    { v: 'B', layer: 2, children: ['C'] },
    { v: 'A', layer: 3, children: ['B'] }
]

Testing

To run the tests for this library, make sure you have Mocha and Chai installed:

bash

npm install
npm test

The tests are located in the test directory and cover various scenarios to ensure the algorithm functions correctly.
Contributing

Contributions are welcome! If you have any ideas, suggestions, or bug reports, please open an issue or submit a pull request.

To contribute:

    Fork the repository.
    Create a new branch for your feature/bugfix.
    Commit your changes and push the branch to your fork.
    Open a pull request to the main repository.

